	(116,3,23,1,'movember','Mo Mondays','','<img src=\"http://media.dfrg.com/_delfriscosgrille/promos/movember-logo.png\" />\n<p>#manupstacheup</p>\n<p>OUR MO MENU: It&rsquo;s Movember at the Grille. We&rsquo;re raising Mo money for men&rsquo;s health, one moustache at a time. For each item ordered from our special Movember menu, we&rsquo;ll donate a percentage of sales to the Movember Foundation.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://media.dfrg.com/_delfriscosgrille/promos/Movember-Menu.pdf\">VIEW MOVEMBER MENU</a></p>\n<p>MOVEMBER &lsquo;STACHE BASH: Kick off Movember at our &lsquo;Stache Bash Friday, November 1st (Palm Beach location  October 31, 2013). Grab some grub and whet your whistle with a Lip Tickler or Stiff Upper Lip. A percentage of sales will be donated to the Movember Foundation for men&rsquo;s health. Together, we can grow above and beyond to help kick cancer in the well, you know.</p>\n <p>MOUSTACHE MONDAYS: Real or faux, flash that &lsquo;stache on Mondays in Movember to get a free appetizer. One app per group of four.</p>\n<p>BEST IN MO PHOTO CONTEST &dash; BEGINNING OCTOBER 26th: Calling all Mo Bros and Mo Sistas, we&rsquo;re looking for the Best in Mo! Visit the Facebook page of your local Del Frisco&rsquo;s Grille location, click on the &ldquo;Best in Mo&rdquo; box and upload a picture of yourself sporting your best moustache or &ldquo;faux mo&rdquo; (that means ladies can enter, too.) for a chance to win dinner for four at the Grille, a year-long health club membership and a grooming package valued at up to $500. Be sure to include a fun title for your photo! Artificial moustaches are allowed. Entries will be collected for each Del Frisco&rsquo;s Grille location on the local Del Frisco&rsquo;s Grille Facebook pages and there will be a winner for every location! Your Facebook friends will vote to select each Best in Mo. <a href=\"http://delfriscosgrille.com/BestinMoRules\" target=\"_blank\">Rules and Regulations</a></p>','http://media.dfrg.com/_delfriscosgrille/promos/movember-mobile-2.jpg','http://media.dfrg.com/_delfriscosgrille/promos/movember-small.png','http://media.dfrg.com/_delfriscosgrille/promos/movember-promo.png',NULL,'','2013-10-23','2013-11-30','mobile-hero','unpublished','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
