VALUES
	(9,1,'Harbor Room','harbor-room','<p>Enjoying sweeping harbor views in our glass walled Harbor Room with patio access. Intimate setting for rehearsal dinners, business meetings or cocktail receptions.</p>','<ul>\n<li>Number of Seats: 32</li>\n<li>Reception Occupancy: 40</li>\n<li>Flat Screen TV</li>\n<li>Audio Visual Capabilities</li>\n<li>Patio</li>\n</ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(10,1,'Doulos Smaller Half','doulos-small','<p>Our Doulos Rooms can be sat separately for smaller events of 15-50 or combined for larger scale events of up to 100 guests. Set off from the main dining room helps to ensure a quiet setting for speakers and built in audio visual makes presentations a breeze. Floor-to-ceiling windows allow for natural light and features the hustle and bustle of the Seaport District.</p>','<ul>\n<li>Number of Seats: 32</li>\n<li>Reception Occupancy: 40</li>\n<li>Flat Screen TV</li>\n<li>Built in Audio Capabilities</li>\n</ul>',NULL,1,'published'),
	(11,1,'Doulos Larger Half','doulos-large','<p>Our Doulos Rooms can be sat separately for smaller events of 15-50 or combined for larger scale events of up to 100 guests. Set off from the main dining room helps to ensure a quiet setting for speakers and built in audio visual makes presentations a breeze. Floor-to-ceiling windows allow for natural light and features the hustle and bustle of the Seaport District.</p>','<ul>\n<li>Number of Seats: 50</li>\n<li>Reception Occupancy: 60</li>\n<li>120&rdquo; Screen &amp; Projector</li>\n<li>Built in Audio Capabilities</li>\n</ul>',NULL,2,'published'),
	(12,3,'Wine Cellar','wine-cellar','Beautifully decorated room surrounded by wine on all four walls. With a stone floor, dark wood wine racks and soft lighting this room is a must for small celebrations and oenophiles! Your guests will be seated at one large table to keep the conversation lively. Kept at an ambiant 62 degrees Fahrenheit, it&rsquo;s perfect for that special event.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 18</li><li>Beautiful Working Wine Cellar</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(13,3,'Comanche','comanche','This expansive private dining room features a flat-screen TV ideal for business presentations or showing a destination wedding video to all your envious friends who couldn\'t attend. Beautifully appointed with built-in wine racks, the Comanche Room is perfect for large events - social or business.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 40</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 75</li><li>Flat Screen TV with connections for laptops and tablets for presentations</li><li>Wine Racks</li></ul>',NULL,1,'published'),
	(14,3,'Reagan','reagan','Our largest, fully-private room, the Reagan Room has a beautiful wine wall, private bar and built-in A/V. This room is ideal for large business presentations, wedding receptions, rehearsal dinners and cocktail receptions before dinner.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 75</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 150</li><li>Built-in LCD and drop down screen</li><li>Private Bar</li><li>Wine Wall and Fireplace</li></ul>',NULL,2,'published'),
	(15,3,'Dakota','dakota','An intimate room perfect for small social events and important business meetings with guests seated at one table boardroom-style for ease of conversation and presentations. This room is perfect for roundtable discussions, board meetings and client dinners.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 16</li><li>Screen Available</li></ul>',NULL,3,'published'),
	(16,3,'Sports','sports','Named for the famed Dallas professional sports teams that make the city a destination as much as its renownded steak houses, this semi-private room features a flat-screen TV suitable for presentations or watching the big game.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 30</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 50</li><li>Flat Screen TV with connections for laptops and tablets for presentations</li></ul>',NULL,4,'published'),
	(17,3,'Viking','viking','A wonderful private space with an intimate feel for groups of 20-30 guests. The Viking Room has a small reception space which flows into the dining area. All guests are seated at one long table for easy conversation. This room is perfect for mid-sized social gatherings and business presentations.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 30</li><li>Small Reception Area</li><li>Screen Available</li></ul>',NULL,5,'published'),
	(18,3,'Lounge','lounge','A semi-private room with an Old World lounge feel, this room enjoys the ambiance of the nearby live piano and five flat-screen TVs lining the walls while a cabinet of cognacs, tequilas and scotches tempt. It&rsquo;s perfect for the sport-lover and connoisseur alike! The Lounge is a must for the game-day action of March Madness, the NFL &amp; NBA drafts, the Olympics, bowl games and the World Series. And it&rsquo;s an ideal setting for networking cocktail receptions.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 70</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 100</li><li>Several Flat Screen TV&rsquo;s</li></ul>',NULL,6,'published'),
	(19,3,'Lincoln','lincoln','One of our main dining rooms, the Lincoln Room can accommodate large parties in a semi-private setting. The room is appointed with a beautiful floor-to-ceiling glass wine wall and a fireplace.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 95</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 200</li><li>Wine Wall and Fireplace</li><li>Screen Available</li></ul>',NULL,7,'published'),
	(20,3,'Rose','rose','A semi-private room separated from the Lincoln Room by a glass wall, the Rose Room is perfect for mid-sized social and business events that want to feel the energy of the main dining room - to see and be seen.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 30</li><li>Glass panes with a view of the main dining room</li></ul>',NULL,8,'published'),
	(21,3,'Lincoln &amp; Rose Rooms','lincoln-rose','This combination of two semi-private dining rooms is perfect for wedding receptions where the wedding party can sit in the glass-enclosed Rose Room with full access to their guests in the Lincoln Room.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 125</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 250</li><li>Wine Wall</li><li>Screen Available</li></ul>',NULL,9,'published'),
	(22,2,'Wine Cellar','wine-cellar','The Wine Cellar features beautiful stone floors, glass walls and wine surrounding the dining space. It is the perfect place for business dinners, presentations, and any social occasion. Create an exceptional event in this gorgeous space by taking full advantage of the private bar and flat screen TVs. The Wine Cellar can be broken into 2 separate rooms that can seat 30-35 guests each for a more intimate gathering.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 70</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 100</li><li>Private Bar</li><li>Flat Screen TV</li><li>Private Floor</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(23,2,'Half Cellar','half-cellar','The Wine Cellar features beautiful stone floors, glass walls and wine surrounding the dining space. It is the perfect place for business dinners, presentations, and any social occasion. Create an exceptional event in this gorgeous space by taking full advantage of the private bar and flat screen TVs. The Wine Cellar can be broken into 2 separate rooms that can seat 30-35 guests each for a more intimate gathering.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 35</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 30</li><li>Flat Screen TV</li><li>Private Floor</li></ul>',NULL,1,'published'),
	(24,2,'Eagle Room','eagle-room','The Eagle Room offers a view from the top for business dinners and social occasions. This semi-private space is located on the Mezzanine level, and while your group can enjoy a more private seating area, they aren\'t far from the action in the Main Dining space and bars.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 20</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 15</li><li>Flat Screen TV</li></ul>',NULL,2,'published'),
	(25,2,'Alcove','alcove','Enjoy a business dinner or social occasion in the Alcove, a semi-private dining space, located on the Main Dining level. This space is perfect for a small business group, birthday, or a bachelorette night out!','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 16</li></ul>',NULL,3,'published'),
	(26,2,'Mezzanine Bar &amp; Dining Space','mezzanine','The Mezzanine level offers beautiful panoramic views of SouthPark that cannot be missed. For large groups this the perfect place to enjoy celebratory business dinners or special occasions. The private bar is a great place to socialize before sitting down and enjoying the views with dinner.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 110</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 150</li><li>Private Bar</li><li>City Views</li></ul>',NULL,4,'published'),
	(27,35,'Esquire','esquire','The Esquire Room is a Wine Room located on the main level of the restaurant. Two of it\'s 4 walls are glass wine storage bins that allow for gorgeous views of the Main Dining Room, Chandalier & Wine Tower. The Esquire Room is the perfect spot for that VIP group that wants to be right in the middle of the action and still have plenty of privacy.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 35</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 35</li><li>Flat Screen TV</li><li>Wine Room</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(28,35,'Oak','oak','The Oak Room is perfect for groups of 6-10. In the Summer months your guests are free to open up the double doors that lead out onto the Terrace overlooking Historic Oak Street. The room also has a large Flat Screen TV for  a presentation.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 10</li><li>Flat Screen TV</li><li>Patio Access</li><li>Views of Oak Street</li></ul>',NULL,1,'published'),
	(29,35,'Eagle 1','eagle-1','The Eagle 1 Room seats up to 40 guests and features a wine storage wall along the back of the room, the large screen and intimate setting make it perfect for bussiness presentations and private dinnners. This room also can also open up to include Eagle 2 and will seat 60 guests useing both adjoining rooms.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 40</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 30</li><li>Flat Screen TV</li><li>Wine Room</li></ul>',NULL,2,'published'),
	(30,35,'Eagle 2','eagle-2','The Eagle 2 Room seats up to 20 guests and has an entire wall of windows that look out onto the 3rd Floor dining room. This room can also be combined with Eagle 1 and will seat up to 60 guests using both adjoining rooms.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 20</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 10</li><li>Flat Screen TV</li><li>Views of Dining Room</li><li>Wine Room</li></ul>',NULL,3,'published'),
	(31,35,'Mezzanine &amp; 3rd Floor Bar','mezzanine','The 3rd Level of the restaurant Houses the Mezzanine Dining Room which can seat up to 180 and has a sepaarte bar space. Your guests can take the elevator directly to this floor and have the entire space to themselves. The large bar os perfect for a cocktail hour before dinner and the fireplace adds to the ambiance as do the windows that overlook Oak Street and the historic Esquire Theatre Sign. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 180</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 300</li><li>Balcony</li><li>Fireplace</li><li>Flat Screens</li></ul>',NULL,4,'published'),
	(32,4,'Colorado','colorado','Wonderful large private space with access to the Denver Tech Center&rsquo;s most popular Cigar Bar and outdoor Patio. The perfect room to host a reception, presentation or rehearsal dinner. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 60</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 75</li><li>Projector and drop down screen</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(33,4,'Dakota','dakota','The perfect room for your presentation or conference.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 34</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 40</li><li>Features two flat screen televisions and a projector</li></ul>',NULL,1,'published'),
	(34,4,'Wine','wine','Lovely space for a celebration dinner or board room luncheon. It has one wall that has a view into our working wine cellar and original Colorado rock walls.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 24</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 30</li><li>Flat screen television with projector</li></ul>',NULL,2,'published'),
	(35,4,'Coulter','coulter','The perfect location to host a board room dinner or presentation.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 28</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 30</li><li>Flat screen television with projector</li><li>Fire Place</li></ul>',NULL,3,'published'),
	(36,4,'Lincoln','lincoln','Large event space for celebration receptions, rehearsal dinners and corporate events.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 78</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 90</li><li>Projector and drop down screen</li></ul>',NULL,4,'published'),
	(37,5,'Fort Worth','fort-worth-room','The Fort Worth Room is located on the 2nd floor and has neutral walls with dark rick mahogany wood accents throughout.  We can accommodate 40 to 80 people and several creative ways to customize the table arrangements for any occasion.  This room is best for wedding rehearsal or reception dinners.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 80</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 250</li><li>Can split into two rooms</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(38,5,'Sports','sports','The Sports Room is located on our 2nd floor.  This room features a beautiful classic marble fireplace.  This room will accommodate 32 to 40 people and is a great room entertainment clients or just watching a sports channel on the huge 60&rdquo; TV.  ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 40</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 60</li><li>Flat Screen TV</li><li>Fire Place</li></ul>',NULL,1,'published'),
	(39,5,'Wine','wine','Our Wine Room is located one floor down from our main dining room.  This room features 4 massive windows that view into our 2 wine cellars.  This is our most requested room that is perfect for any occasion.  Will accommodate up to 26 people.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 26</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 20</li><li>In the Middle of our Wine Cellars</li></ul>',NULL,2,'published'),
	(40,5,'Wheat','wheat','The Wheat Room is located one floor down from our main dining room.  This is the most private and secluded room we have to offer.  This room has a 48&rdquo; TV that can be used for presentations or slideshows. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 26</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 20</li><li>Flat Screen TV</li></ul>',NULL,3,'published'),
	(41,5,'Syndicate','syndicate','The Syndicate Room is located one floor down from our main floor, between the Wine Room and Wheat Room. Perfect for small business or social dinners.  Seats up to 10 on a round table or 14 on a long table. Has a 48&rdquo; TV great for all business occasions, bachelor parties, or watching a football game.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 14</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 15</li><li>Flat Screen TV</li></ul>',NULL,4,'published'),
	(42,5,'Upper Deck/Patio','upperdeck','Our newly added outdoor 2nd floor patio seats up to 45 people. This is a great area to host cocktail parties or baby showers on nice days.  The view of downtown is amazing at night especially at sunset.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 45</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 80</li><li>Outside Seating</li></ul>',NULL,5,'published'),
	(43,5,'Mezzanine - Semi Private','mezzanine','The Mezzaine in located on the 2nd floor of our restaurant.  This area has one of  the best views Del Frisco\'s has to offer, over looking our main dining floor.  This wonderful table can seat up to 22 people on one long table.  Great for small intimate wine tasting dinners, family graduation dinners or birthday parties.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 22</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 30</li><li>Best View</li></ul>',NULL,6,'published'),
	(45,6,'The Wine Cellar','the-wine-cellar','Beautiful Italian Stone floor, surrounded with glass enclosed wine cellar. Perfect room for a dinner or a reception. The room can also be divided in to 3 smaller rooms with each seating 36 guests.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 106</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 150</li><li>Glassed in Wine Cellar</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(46,6,'The Houston Room','the-houston-room','Located on the first floor, The Houston room is perfect for an intimate dinner or smaller business meetings. This room can also be divided in to 2 smaller rooms seating 8 in each room.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 20</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 22</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(47,6,'The Texans Room','the-texans-room','The Texans room is filled with memorabelia of the Houston Texans. The granite table top surrounded with leather high back chairs, creates the perfect ambiance for your dinner or business lunch.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 16</li><li>Flat Screen</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(48,7,'Comanche','comanche','Private space perfect for an intimate reception or a business dinner. Located in a very secluded area of the restaurant. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 30</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 30</li><li>50-inch Flat Screen</li><li>Complete Private Space with 2 Doors</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(49,7,'Dakota','dakota','Intimate meeting space for small groups. Upgraded ceiling and lighting features along with a large sized mirror. Comes equipped with 50\' flat screen television for Audio/Visual needs. Room has double-doors for increased privacy. Perfect space for company and executive meetings. Dakota over looks the small wine cellar.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 30</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 20</li><li>50- inch Flat Screen  </li><li>Over looking our small wine cellar</li><li>Close to the main bar</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(50,7,'Full Nevada','nevada','Largest available private dining space. Can accommodate up 150 guests. Room features modern art work and lighting. Drop down screen is available for Audio/Visual needs. Perfect space for wedding rehearsal dinners and receptions. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 140</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 150</li><li>Drop Down Screen</li><li>Largest Private Space</li><li>Chandeliers </li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(51,7,'Nevada 1','nevada-2','Room seats up to 45 guests. Enclosed with double doors for complete privacy. Recommended for business dinners, birthday celebrations and executive events.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 50</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 50</li><li>Eclosed Private Room</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(52,7,'Nevada 2','nevada-3','Room seats up 45 guests. Enclosed with double doors. Room comes equppied with drop down screen and is best suited for pharmaceutical dinners and business events.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 50</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 50</li><li>Enclosed Private Room</li><li>Drop Down Screen</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(53,7,'Coulter','coulter','Room seats up to 40 guests. Open space with no doors. Room is conveniently located near restroom and kitchen.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 40</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 40</li><li>Open Space overlooking Main Dining</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(54,7,'Sports Room','sports-room',NULL,'<ul><li>Number of Seats: 50</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 60</li><li>3 TV\'s inside the private space</li><li>Humidor inside room</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(55,7,'Lincoln','lincoln','Room seats up to 60 guests. Open space with no doors, overlooking the main dining and bar area. James Bond table is viewable from dining space and located near the Cigar Patio,','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 60</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 70</li><li>James Bond Table outside of the room</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(56,7,'Wine Cellar','wine-cellar','Most exclusive room in the restaurant. Located adjacent to the large wine cellar with large glass wall dividing the space. Secluded and equipped with double doors for privacy. Can seat up to 16 guests at one table or 20 guest at two tables side-by-side. Ideal for wedding receptions, bachelor/bacheloretter parties, birthdays, or corporate events.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 20</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 30</li><li>Floor to ceiling glass window over-looking the wine cellar room</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(57,7,'Patio','patio','Patio seats up to 12 guest, at 3 round tables with an extended lounge space. Guests can enjoy cigars during dinner. Space comes equipped with television, heaters, misters, and full length curtains.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 12</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 30</li><li>50-inch Flat Screen outside of the restaurant</li><li>Misters and Heaters</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(58,8,'Wine Cellar','wine-cellar','Most exclusive private room on it\'s own floor in our Wine Cellar.  Showcases Del Frisco\'s Old and New world wines.  Complete with high ceilings and stone floors, this room is sure to impress.  The room can accommodate up to 80 guests for a sit down dinner.  When utilizing both the Wine Cellar and the private bar can accommodate up to 150 guests for a standing reception.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 80</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 150</li><li>Built in Audio Capabilities</li><li>Private Bar</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(59,8,'Half Cellar ','half-cellar','Wine Cellar can be divided into two halves with a wooden air wall to create two separate rooms each with their own entrance.  Each half can accomomdate up to 40 guests at round tables or 22 at one table.  ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 40</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 50</li><li>Flat Screen TV</li><li>Built in Audio Capabilities</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(60,8,'Diamond Room','diamond-room','Located on the main floor, this is an ideal room for presentations and meeting functions.  This room can accommodate up to 28 guests at separate tables or 22 for one table. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 28</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 35</li><li>Flat Screen TV</li><li>Built in Audio Capabilities</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(61,8,'Newsroom','newsroom','Located on the Mezzanine level with a spectacular view of Sixth Avenue, this balcony space is perfect for events looking to experiencing the energy and vibe of the city while maintaining your own exclusive space.  The space can accommodate up to 35 guests in round tables for 22 at one table. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 35</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 50</li><li>Restaurant Ambiance</li><li>City views</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(62,8,'Lounge','lounge','Located behind the Newsroom on the Mezzanine level, the Lounge is a fully private enclosed room boasting a full wall of floor to ceiling windows.  This private room features city views and has an old-world feeling perfectly suited for business meetings or social gatherings.  The room can accommodate 60 guests at separate tables or 45 guests at one table. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 60</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 75</li><li>Floor to Ceiling Windows</li><li>City Views</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
