	(73,11,'The Wine Room','the-wine-room','The Wine Room feature an elegant wine wall as you enter as a focal piece. It\'s ability to be private or semi private and just off the dining room floor gives it that better than the rest experience. Perfect for business or socail and certainly anything else you might come up with.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 75</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 100</li><li>Wine Wall</li><li>Ramp Entrance &amp; Stairs</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(74,11,'Front Wine Room','front-wine-room','The Front Wine Room features a perfect option for business luncheons and intimate family dinners.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 18</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 25</li><li>Easy Access Entry</li><li>Just off the dining room</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(75,11,'Back Wine Room','back-wine-room','The Back Wine Room just above the main dining room floor features a beautiful accent wine wall with textured windows that make for private or semi private events. A favorite of many this room is best for large gatherings receptions and holiday dinners. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 40</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 50</li><li>Accent Wine Wall</li><li>Ramp</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(76,11,'Colorado','colorado','Colorado Street Room is The favorite for any business affair, reception or celebration dinner. It features a beautiful accent wall with the privacy of four walls and a little natural light that comes from the hallway entrance of side bar yet far enough off from the main dining you wouldn\'t even know it was there.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 25</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 35</li><li>Flat Screen TV</li><li>Accent Wine Wall</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(77,11,'ATX','atx','ATX Room features soft lighting and a warm fireplace as a focal point when you walk in. This room has just the right amount of privacy for any business meeting or group that\'s getting ready to hit the town after a great steak!','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 25</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 35</li><li>Fireplace</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(78,11,'TownLake','townlake','Townlake Room has many features! A Flat Screen for smaller presentations and a drop down screen for making a statement. This room also features the accent wine wall behind the drop down screen that makes for a great eye catcher. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 25</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 35</li><li>Flat Screen & Drop-Down Jumbo Screen</li><li>Projector</li></ul></li><li>Accent Wine Wall</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(79,11,'The Capital ','the-capital','The capital is the meca of Colorado Street, ATX, and The Townlake Room. Anything and everything these rooms can offer the Captial room provides with more space. Seating up to 120, it\'s a favorite for receptions, rehearsal dinners, and large presentations. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 120</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 200</li><li>2 Flate Screen Tvs & Drop Down Jumbo Screen</li><li>Projector</li></ul></li><li>Fireplace</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(80,11,'Side Bar','side-bar','Sullys Side Bar, newly renovated and my personal favorite! Features semi private and private events. From receptions & cocktail events, to elegant sit down dinners. A private bar and views of 3rd and Colorado this room adds that certain something and is quickly becoming a favorite of others. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 65</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 100</li><li>7 Flat Screens & Private Bar</li><li>Beautiful View of Downtown Austin</li><li>Natural Lighting &amp; It&rsquo;s own entrance</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(81,10,'Private Dining Room','private-dining-room','This quiet, out-of-the-way room is perfect for hosting business meetings and presentations as well as intimate celebrations for family and friends. The Flat Screen TV can be used for Powerpoint presentations or photo slideshows or even to view concerts and sporting events.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 30</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 30</li><li>42&rdquo; Flat Screen TV</li><li>Wi-Fi</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(82,10,'Library','library','The Library is available as a private space but can also be subdivied into two semi-private spaces. The layout is flexible and can be adjusted to comfortably accommodate groups of 10 - 30 guests without excess empty space. It is a perfect space for rehearsal dinners, retirement celebrations, and birthday parties.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 50</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 65</li><li>Wi-Fi</li><li>Two access points</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(83,12,'Oriole','oriole','The Oriole Room is our VIP room. This room will seat up to 6 guests at a round table. This is the first space as you enter the dining room. There is a flat screen television in this space with the connections for a PC laptop. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 6</li><li>Flat Screen TV</li><li>Two walls of windows</li><li>Connections of Laptop</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(84,12,'Raven','raven','The Raven Room will seat up to 15 guests at one long table. This room is located in the front of the restaurant off of the main dining room. It has a wall of windows with views of Light Street and the harbor shops. The Raven room also has a flat screen television with connections for a PC laptop. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 15</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 15</li><li>Flat Screen TV</li><li>Wall of Windows</li><li>Connections of Laptop</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(85,12,'Ripken','ripken','The Ripken Room will seat up to 10 guests. This is a small private room perfect for an intimate meeting. The room is equipped with a flat screen television with the connections for a PC laptop. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 10</li><li>Flat Screen TV</li><li>Wall of Windows</li><li>Connections of Laptop</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(86,12,'Mednansky','mednansky','The Mednansky Room will seat up to 20 guests at one long table or 25 at multiple smaller tables. This room is ideal for meetings as it is located near the back of the restaurant. The Mednansky room has a flat screen television with the connections for a PC laptop. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 20</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 25</li><li>Flat Screen TV</li><li>Quietest space</li><li>Connections of Laptop</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(87,12,'Harborview','harborview','The Harborview Room will seat up to 35 guests at two long tables. This room is located off of our bar and lounge area. It has access to our patio, weather permitting. The live jazz music can be heard from this space. It is the ideal room for a social event. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 35</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 50</li><li>Flat Screen TV</li><li>Patio Access</li><li>Connections of Laptop</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(88,12,'Library','library','The Library is our largest space which will seat up to 60 guests at round tables. This room is semi private only because it does not have a door that closes. This room is great for large group dinners or cocktail receptions. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 60</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 75</li><li>Wine Wall</li><li>Wall can open to view Main Dining Room</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(89,13,'MARTINI ROOM','martInI-room','Room has separate lighting and music controls. Room has flat screen television available for use at no charge. This may also be used for presentations. Available for private parties from 8 to 40 guests for a seated dinner or 50 guests cocktail style. Great for Business Meetings, Lunch Parties, Small Presentations, Bridal Showers, Birthday Parties, etc.\r','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 40</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 50</li><li>Flat Screen TV- Can hook up to a laptop for presentation or play cable television</li><li>Built in Audio Capabilities using Flat Screen. Room has it\'s own lighting and volume control for house music</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(90,13,'RINGSIDE','rIngsIde','Room can accommodate screen/ projection presentations, large or small bands, Ipod hook-up & TV projection. Available for private parties from 10 to 85 guests for a seated dinner. Ringside is also the perfect location for cocktail parties and will accommodate up to 200 guests. Great for Business Lunches, Large Presentations, Holiday Parties, Cocktail Parties, Engagement Parties, Football Games, etc.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 85</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 200</li><li>Built-in Bar</li><li>Stage for Band, DJ, etc.</li><li>Ipod Hook-up for personal music</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(91,13,'LIBRARY','lIbrary','Room has separate lighting and music controls. Room has two flat screen televisions with sound capablities available for use at no charge. This may also be used for presentations. Available for private and semi-private parties from 8 to 110 guests for a seated dinner or 150 guests cocktail style.  Room can be divided into two seperate semi-private areas using a pipe and drape allowing for a smaller space that can seat up to 25 and a larger than can seat up to 60. Great for Large Presentations, Business Meetings, Lunch  Parties, Rehearsal Dinners, Holiday Parties, etc.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 110</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 150</li><li>Two Flat Screen TV- Can hook up to a laptop for presentation or play cable television</li><li>Built in Audio Capabilities using Flat Screen. Room has it&rsquo;s own lighting and volume control for house music</li><li>Frosted windows are removable allowing for either a completely private event or for your group to be seperated yet still part of the main dining room\'s energetic feel. </li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(92,14,'PDR 1','pdr-1','<p>It\'s the perfect place to host a rehearsal dinner, business luncheon, or even a ladies night out. Create a one-of-a-kind experience with the use of our flat screen TV, simple audio connections and various room layout options. With access to patio, this space provides an outdoor experience to have your cocktails and appetizers.</p>','<ul>\n<li>Number of Seats: 64</li>\n<li>Reception Occupancy: 85</li>\n<li>70&rdquo; Flat Screen TV, 3-42&rdquo; Flat Screen</li>\n<li>Built in Audio Capitibilites</li>\n<li>Access to Patio</li>\n</ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(93,14,'PDR 2','pdr-2','Great enviroment for those smaller lunch or dinner meetings, and family celebrations. Private space in the upper dining room with private entrance.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 12</li><li>Round table for 8</li><li>Ramp</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(94,14,'PDR 2/3','pdr-2/3','<p>Just up the ramp in the upper dining room, this space gives you a chance to still hear the live band from the bar. You will get to experience the upper dining room with ease as you entertain your business guests, celebrate the anniversary with your family, or create a memorable dining experience for the holiday\'s.</p>','<ul>\n<li>Number of Seats: 20 with presentation; 25 without presentation&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Reception Occupancy: 30</li>\n<li>Wine Wall Feature</li>\n<li>Private Windows</li>\n<li>Projection Screen</li>\n</ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(95,14,'PDR 3','pdr-3','Enjoy the being in the middle of everything. The space gives you a semi-private space or private space for a small gathering while enjoying the upper dining area. With our privacy windows in you can have a quiet evening or choose to take the windows out to enjoy being the center of attention. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 14</li><li>Wine Wall Feature</li><li>Private Windows</li><li>Projection Screen</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(96,14,'PDR 3/4','pdr-3/4','<p>Private entrance with presentation capabilities. Private Dining or Semi-Private area for engagement parties, business celebrations, or birthday parties. Great space to have cocktails and appetizer party with the wonderful conversation starter with our wine wall.</p>','<ul>\n<li>Number of Seats:&nbsp;20 with presentation; 25 without presentation&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Reception Occupancy: 30</li>\n<li>Wine Wall Feature</li>\n<li>Private Windows</li>\n<li>Projection Screen</li>\n</ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(97,14,'PDR 4','pdr-4','Great enviroment for those smaller lunch or dinner meetings, and family celebrations. Private space in the upper dining room with private entrance.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 10</li><li>Projection Screen</li><li>Private Windows</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(98,14,'Patio','patio','Be part of it all! The covered patio space allows you to be at the hottest spot in Charlotte in the SouthEnd Community. Enjoy a seat down dinner or some cocktails and appetizers as you breathe in the outdoors. The space is equipped with heaters to ease the cooler nights of Charlotte. Enjoy the game on the flat screen TV\'s while having your favorite cigar.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 80</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 125</li><li>Covered Patio</li><li>Heated in Winter</li><li>Flat Screen TV&rsquo;s</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(99,14,'Bar Alcove','bar-alcove','Your own little corner of paradise. Be the VIP of our bar! Enjoy your private dining experience with some light hors d\'oeuvres and cocktails, prior to dining with us.  Heading into downtown? Start your night off here prior to your celebration and enjoy front row seating to our live band. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 9</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 15</li><li>Flat Screen TV&rsquo;s</li><li>Live Band</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(100,15,'River North','river-north','The River North Room, located on the 2nd level of Sullivan\'s Steakhouse Chicago (accessible via stairs and/or elevator), overlooks the vibrant intersection of Hubbard and Dearborn streets.  Perfect for groups of 15-30, River North features a beautiful custom wine wall and is a great spot for both business events and social engagements.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 36</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 50</li><li>Flat Screen Television</li><li>Two Full Walls of Windows</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(101,15,'River West / River East','river-west-east','The River West and River East rooms combined, located on the 2nd level of Sullivan\'s Steakhouse Chicago (accessible via stairs and/or elevator), are our largest private dining option for a sit-down meal, and feature two flatscreen televisions as well as complimentary wireless microphone capabilities.  This private dining space, which overlooks Hubbard Street, can also be split into two separate spaces, each seating up to 30 guests, and each featuring a flatscreen television.  ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 60</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 120</li><li>Flat Screen Television(s)</li><li>Wireless Microphone Capability</li><li>One Full Wall of Windows</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(102,15,'Streeterville','streeterville','Streeterville, located on the 2nd level of Sullivan\'s Steakhouse Chicago (accessible via stairs and/or elevator), is the perfect space for an intimate business meeting or dinner, as 4-10 guests will be very comfortable and able to share a great meal over lively conversation or private business matters.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 12</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 16</li><li>Flat Screen Television</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(103,15,'Boardroom','boardroom','The Boardroom, located on the 2nd level of Sullivan\'s Steakhouse Chicago (accessible via stairs and/or elevator), is an amazing option for up to 16 guests and overlooks Dearborn Street.  Adjacent to the Lounge area, the Boardroom offers smaller groups the much desired privacy of a banquet room in an appropriately-sized space.  ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 16</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 20</li><li>Flat Screen Television</li><li>Two Full Walls of Windows</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(104,15,'Lounge','lounge','The semi-private Lounge space,  located on the 2nd level of Sullivan\'s Steakhouse Chicago (accessible via stairs and/or elevator) and available for exclusive reservation, features a gorgeous built-in private bar, banquette seating and the option for both seating tables and \"high-top\" cocktail tables.  Perfect as pre-function space for appetizers and cocktails before moving into a private dining room for dinner or for a cocktail reception or networking event unto its own, the Lounge space is sure to please any group - business or pleasure! ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 60</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 120</li><li>Flat Screen Television</li><li>Private Bar</li><li>One Full Wall of Windows</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(105,17,'Library','library','Whether you are planning an intimate dinner for two, a social gathering for friends or a business presentation for fifty, the Library offers dark mahogany d_cor and custom floor plans to set the perfect ambiance.  Complete with state-of-the-art audio/visual equipment, advance your private dinner to a full experience with background photos, videos or an impressive presentation.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 50, 45 AV</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 75</li><li>55&rdquo; HDMI Screen</li><li>Mobile Boardroom Speakers with 2 Lavaliere Microphones and hardwire internet access</li><li>Windows open to view main dining room from upper level (optional)</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(106,17,'Sidecar','sidecar','The Sidecar Room is a quiet space perfect for a formal business presentation or a secluded space for engagement dinners.  A favorite for daytime events, this room offers the most natural sunlight of our three private spaces. Large enough for a cocktail reception prior to dinner, this room is the perfect setting for any style of event.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 30, 25 AV</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 45</li><li>55&rdquo; HDMI Screen</li><li>Mobile Boardroom Speakers with 2 Lavaliere Microphones and hardwire internet access</li><li>Full bank of windows allow for natural sunlight during daytime events and city light view during evening dinners</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(107,17,'Jazz Lounge','jazz-lounge','With the glass accordion wall closed, enjoy a private dinner with live music in the background!  Open the accordion wall and be a VIP extension of our Jazz bar!  This room is perfect for birthday soirees, bachelor(ette) parties or a fun night of music and entertainment after a long day in conference.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 28</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 45</li><li>Adjacent to nightly live Jazz 6-10pm </li><li>Glass accordion wall</li></ul></li><li>Cable TV (no sound)</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(108,17,'Main Dining','main-dining','Enjoy exclusive service for your large group by reserving the whole restaurant!  We will customize your floor plan, wine-paired menu, d_cor and entertainment.  Close the office for the afternoon and enjoy a development retreat in style or invite your closest friends and family for a casino night in our three private rooms!  The sky is the limit and we dare you to share your best ideas for how we can help make your event unforgettable. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 165</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 300</li><li>Exlcusive service in main dining room plus all private spaces</li><li>Custom floor plan, music and entertainment</li><li>Expo kitchen</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(109,17,'Patio','patio','Sit back and relax with full dinner service or after-dinner cigars in our intimate outdoor lounge.  The Patio can be paired with another of our private spaces to allow your group an indoor/outdoor party!  Perfect for a martini on summer\'s eve or a sip of Scotch in a winter wonderland!','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 40</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 75</li><li>Can be paired with private room reservation for indoor/outdoor event</li><li>Lounge couches and seated tables</li><li>Heaters for winter events</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(110,18,'BOARDROOM','boardroom','Very cozy &amp; private. Perfect for small meetings or family gatherings.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 30</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 30</li><li>Flat Screen TV</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(111,18,'WINEROOM','wIneroom','Just adjacent to the main floor, perfect for an elegant business meeting or special occasion.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 65</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 100</li><li>Beautiful Wine Wall</li><li>Can be split in Half</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
