	(118,19,'Front Wine Room','front-wine-room','This room is perfect for presentations, meetings and other social events.  4 walls and a door offer a private setting and various table layouts are available.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 30</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 40</li><li>Flatscreen</li><li>4 walls and a door</li><li>private or semi-private</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(119,19,'Middle Wine Room','middle-wine-room','The Wine Room has a beautiful wine display and a television.  You have the option of viewing the main dining room by opening the beveled glass wall.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 40</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 50</li><li>Flatscreen</li><li>Wine Display</li><li>private or semi-private</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(120,19,'Back Wine Room','back-wine-room','This room is perfect for smaller groups that still need audio visual for presentations or celebrations.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 18</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 20</li><li>Flatscreen</li><li>Wheelchair access</li><li>private or semi-private</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(121,19,'Fireside Room','fireside-room','The Fireside Room has beautiful wood accents, a fireplace, 2 walls of windows covered with Mecca blinds.  There are 2 televisions in the room that can sync for slideshows and presentations.  ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 75</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 100</li><li>Flatscreen</li><li>Fireplace</li></ul></li><li>2 walls of windows</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(122,20,'PRIVATE DINING ROOM','private-dining-room','Has french doors leading out to our patio making it easy enjoy a cocktail hour outside before your dinner.  The built in A/V equipment is complimentary.  Perfect for business dinners, meetings and presetations or for larger special occassions and holiday parties.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 50</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 70</li><li>Flat Screen TV</li></ul></li><li>Built in Audio Capabilities</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(123,20,'WINE ROOM','wine-room','This room has the ability to be sectioned off into either 2 smaller spaces (one seating up to 22 and one seating up to 56) or 3 smaller spaces (one seating up to 22, one seating up to 36 and one seating up to 18).  The room as a whole is great for large celebrations and the smaller sections are perfect for more intimate business dinners.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 80</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 110</li><li>Back-lit wine wall</li><li>Windows that can be opened fully or partially if desired to bring in energy from the main dining room.</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(124,20,'PATIO','patio','Wonderful outdoor dining space for casual cocktail parties and full sit down dinners alike.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 45</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 65</li><li>2 Flat Screen TVs</li><li>Heaters and fans to aid in temperature control</li><li>Fully covered</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
