	(128,21,'All three Private Dining Rooms','private-dining-rooms','<p>This room is great for rehearsal dinners, business meetings and holiday parties. It has various room layout options and use of both flat screen TVs.</p>','<ul>\n<li>Number of Seats: 80</li>\n<li>Reception Occupancy: 100</li>\n</ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(129,21,'Library','library','The Library is great for cocktail style receptions, holiday dinners and celebratory dinners.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 65</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 80</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(130,21,'Patio ','patio','<p>The patio is perfect for cocktail style receptions, cigar/scotch dinners, birthday parties, and bachelorette parties.</p>','<ul>\n<li>Number of Seats: 60</li>\n<li>Reception Occupancy: 100</li>\n<li>Heated Patio</li>\n<li>Covered Patio</li>\n</ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(131,22,'Lakeside','lakeside','Our elegant and secluded Lakeside room is an inviting dining area with patio access that boasts full A/V capabilities perfect for business presentatations, birthday parties, or cocktail receptions.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 32</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 50</li><li>Flat Screen Television</li><li>Built in A/V Capabilities</li><li>Patio Access with Landscaped Pond View</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(132,22,'NAPA','napa','Napa&rsquo;s soft lighting and personal fireplace accent this beautiful private dining space  From the two large wall-mount flatscreen televisions, to the easy patio access, this room is perfect for luncheons, wedding rehearsal dinners, &amp; business meetings alike .','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 45</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 60</li><li>2 Flat Screen Televisions</li><li>Built in A/V Capabilities</li><li>Patio Access with Landscaped Pond View &amp; Private Fireplace</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(133,22,'SONOMA','sonoma','Two walls of windows invite plenty of light in for any daytime function in our Sonoma room.  Perfect for wedding, bridal, or baby showers this space also brings style & candle-light to dinners & social gatherings in the evening.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 45</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 60</li><li>2 Flat Screen Televisions</li><li>Built in A/V Capabilities</li><li>2 Walls of Windows with Landscaped View &amp; Private Fireplace</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(134,22,'WINE COUNTRY','wIne-coUntry','As beautiful as its namesake, the Wine Country room is perfect for any large gathering.  With four large A/V capable flatscreen televisions, no guest will miss a moment of your presentation. Two private fireplaces and patio access make this space the place to be any night of the week. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 90</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 150</li><li>4 Flat Screen Televisions</li><li>Built in A/V Capabilities</li><li>Patio Access with 2 Private Fireplaces</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(135,22,'Tower (semi-private)','tower','The Tower room offers semi-private functionability with the full dining experience of being in the restaurant.  With a view of our stunning 2-story wine cellar, vaulted ceilings, and a high energy atmosphere, this room is the perfect spot for any cocktail reception or dinner with collegues & friends.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 40</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 50</li><li>2-Story Wine Room</li><li>Vaulted Ceilings</li><li>Booth &amp; Table Seating</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(136,22,'Side Lounge (semi-private)','side-lounge','Our exhuberent Lounge area offers high-energy with high-top tables, couches, and live music seven nights a week all while your guests enjoy semi-private function.  Several large flatscreen televisions ensure that the big game won\'t be missed during your cocktail party or night out with the girls.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 58</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 120</li><li>2 Flat Screen Televisions</li><li>Live Music</li><li>Easy Bar Access</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(137,23,'Library (Semi-Private)','library','<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Come be a part of Naperville and sit in our board room, completely enclosed with windows, it&rsquo;s the perfect space to host your celebration and enjoy the scenery Naperville has to offer. The room also features a 70&rdquo; plasma and full AV capabilities at no charge; great for business meetings and presentations.</span></p>','<ul type=\"disc\">\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Number of Seats: 75</span></li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Reception Occupancy: 100</span></li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>70&rdquo; flat screen full AV</span></li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Enclosed with open and shut windows</span></li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Next to bar area</span></li>\n</ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(138,23,'Executive Boardroom','executive-boardroom','<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span  7.5pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">Overlook our dining room and enjoy the scenery. The large space offers a mixture of booth and table seating along the wine wall.</span></p>','<ul type=\"disc\">\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span  7.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Number of Seats: 25</span></li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span  7.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Reception Occupancy: 35</span></li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span  7.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Glass sliding doors</span></li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span  7.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Built-in wine case</span></li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span  7.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Booth seating</span></li>\n</ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(139,24,'Upstairs Boardroom','Upstairs-boardroom','Our main level boardroom is the perfect space to host a business meeting or family get together for as large as 16 or as intimate as 6 as this room has the capability to divide into two completely private rooms with their own entrances and exits.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 16</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 20</li><li>55&rdquo; LED Flat Screen TV</li><li>Wi-fi</li><li>Hard Wire</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(140,24,'Library','library','Our Library is the perfect location to host a live satellite broadcast!','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 36</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 40</li><li>Wi-fi</li><li>Hard Wire</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(141,24,'Executive Boardroom','executive-boardroom','Our executive boardroom is the best man cave in Omaha!  Perfect spot to watch the game with the guys while enjoying a cold beer or your favorite bottle of wine with the juiciest and most flavorful steak in town!','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 12</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 15</li><li>42&rdquo; Flat Screen TV</li><li>Wi-fi</li><li>Hard Wire</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(142,24,'Wine Cellar','wine-cellar','Our wine cellar is truly one-of-a-kind!  It\'s the perfect place to host your rehearsal dinner with a private bar and restrooms as well as a beautiful escalator/elevator entrance.  Our cellar also have the capability to divide into two completely private rooms with their own entrances and exits.  Complimentary audio/visual is also available.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 80</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 120</li><li>Two 55&rdquo; LED Flat Screen TVs</li><li>Wi-fi</li><li>Hard Wire</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(143,25,'Private Dining Room','private-dining-room','The Private Dining Room is a fully private room with floor to celing windows that overlook the majestic Santa Rosa Mountains. Its large boardroom style table makes it the perfect room for business dinners, presentions and even birthday parties!','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 24</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 35</li><li>Portable projector and screen available</li><li>Hard wired internet</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(144,25,'Library','library','Sitting slightly above the main dining room, the Library is the perfect room to celebrate with you friends, family members and colleagues. With the frosted glass window partitions open you can have a fully private event or keep them open for a view into the main dining room.  ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 50</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 65</li><li>Portable projector and screen available</li><li>3 large half round booths, and mulitple individual tables</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(145,25,'Main Dining Room','main-dining-room','Available private or semi-private, the main dining room can accommodate your groups needs perfectly. With seventeen lush booths surrounding an open floor plan, the main dining room is perfect for your next  celebration, wedding reception, luncheon or more. With your ideas and our creativity, we can perfectly customize the main dining room for each individual event. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 156</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 220</li><li>Features booth and table seating</li><li>Large floral arrangement in the center of the room</li><li>View of the kitchen line and wine room</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(146,26,'Capital Room','capital-room','With a 72inch flat screen TV, built in audio equipment, and wireless internet access our fully private rooms; the Capital Room and the Mason Room,  make for the ideal spaces to host a business meeting or presentation.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 30</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 40</li><li>72 inch flat screen TV </li><li>Built in Audio</li><li>Wireless Internet Access</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(147,26,'Triangle Room ','triangle-room','Double doors lead you into the Triangle Room and your attention is immediately turned to the wall of books. Full of charm, the room has a versitile layout for up to 25 but can boasts the ability to open up to the Capital Room and Mason room for seating up to 100. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 25</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 30</li><li>Wall of vintage books</li><li>Built in Audio</li><li>Wireless Internet Access</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(148,26,'Mason Room','mason-room','SEE CAPITAL ROOM DESCRIPTION. **These rooms are identical in set up and d_cor. I was hoping the description can include both of the rooms. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 30</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 40</li><li>72 inch flat screen TV</li><li>Built in Audio</li><li>Wireless Internet Access</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(149,26,'Canes Room (Semi Private)','canes-room','The perfect mix of black and white photos and extensive wine wall, the Canes Room is the perfect back drop for any occasion.  Not only is there room for mingling but the built in booth seating allows for an intimate setting to enjoy your meal.  ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 75</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 85</li><li>Wine Wall</li><li>Built in Audio</li><li>Wireless Internet Access</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(150,26,'Glenwood Room (Back Bar)','glenwood-room',' Located immediately off of the lounge, the Glenwood Room allows you to be part of our electric bar atmosphere but gives you the privacy to enjoy the company of your guests.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 25</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 35</li><li>Immediately off the bar and lounge </li><li>Built in Audio</li><li>Wireless Internet Access</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(151,27,'Symphony Room','symphony-room','Entertain with complete confidence in our exclusive Symphony Room. In addition to the private dining space, your guests can enjoy the ovation balcony over looking the court yards beautiful waterfall and seasonally illuminated trees. Enjoy a corporate dinner or reception, your rehearsal dinner, a private business meeting, or that special celebration... ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 75</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 100</li><li>Ovation Balcony</li><li>65 inch flat screen tv</li><li>Service station and private restroom</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(152,27,'Theater Room','theater-room','The Theater Rooms is both technological and timeless. The addition of the drop down projector and screen makes it the perfect location for your next lunch or dinner meeting. With a retractable wall you can enjoy the social atmosphere of the bar while giving your guests the private dining experience and service.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 50</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 80</li><li>Drop Down Projector</li><li>Drop Down 8 foot Screen</li><li>retractable wall for more social experience if desired</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(153,28,'The Library','the-library','Size of Private Dining Facilities:\rOur private dining room, The Library, offers private and semi-private dining for parties of 10 to 75 guests for rehearsal dinners, receptions, showers, business luncheons or dinners, presentations, or just a special occasion with no room fee or minimum.  We can also accommodate larger parties on the Main Floor.  We offer complete custom packages for all of your dining needs and can accommodate any special request. \r\rSpecial Amenities:\rSullivanÍs d_cor contains elements of art deco design, rich mahogany wood, crisp white linens, and fresh flowers.  Live Jazz music is played in the bar every night of the week and throughout the restaurant and patio.  Complementary valet parking is offered.  Audio-visual equipment can also be arranged through SullivanÍs.\r','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 75</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 100</li><li>In-house scren and projector</li><li>Internet Access</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(154,29,'Library','library','Our Library features a stone wine wall. Has room for 80 people seated, with the option of seperating into 3 semi private rooms. Our left library can seat 20, Center Library can seat 50, and Right Library can seat 10. Pefect for customizing parites of any size. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 80</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 100</li><li>Stone Wine Wall</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(155,29,'Patio','patio','Our patio is perfect for hosting cocktail parties. Well shaded for those warm summer days, with heaters to keep the party going all year long! Both full menu and happy hour specials are available on the patio. Cigars are also available for purchase to enjoy on the patio. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 50</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 100</li><li>Heaters</li><li>Live Music on weekends</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(156,30,'Buckhead Room','buckhead','<p>Our Buckhead Room is a beautiful space that\'s great for a quiet business meeting or a lively engagement party.</p>','<ul>\n<li>Number of Seats: 49</li>\n<li>Reception Occupancy: 60</li>\n<li>2 Flat Screen TVs.</li>\n<li>Built in Audio Capabalities</li>\n</ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(157,30,'Peachtree Room (Semi-Private)','peachtree',NULL,'<ul><li>Number of Seats: 50</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 50</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(158,30,'Down Stairs Patio-Terrace','patio','Our Terrace is the perect place to host a cocktail party in the heart of Buckhead or enjoy alfrescos dining for up to 32.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 32</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 75</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(159,31,'Room 1976','room-1976','Whether you looking to host business meeting or a night out with friends, Room 1976 will have all the qualities you seek for the perfect intimate event, while still engaging the uptown vibe your looking for.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 20</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 48</li><li>55&rdquo; Flat screen TV</li><li>AV capabilities </li><li>Intimate setting</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(160,31,'McKinney (Upstairs)','mckinney','Our 2nd floor is the perfect venue to host your next Big Event.  The McKinney is the perfect place if you\'re looking for a 4 course dinner or a vivacious Cocktail Party. With access to our second level balcony, you can enjoy the evening under the Texas stars while capturing the atmosphere that Uptown has to offer.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 80</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 116</li><li>private bar</li><li>2nd level balcony access with shaded booths &Misters for those warm Texas evening and a glowing Fireplace.</li><li>5 flat screens TV</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(161,34,'Wine Room','wine-room','Private dining room has two glass walls lined with our extensive wine collection. It is perfect for a business meeting, rehearsal dinner, or a night out with friends. ','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 26</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 45</li><li>LCD flat panel tv/microphone</li><li>audio</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(162,34,'Mezzanine','mezzanine','Our semi-private space is located directly outside of our open layout kitchen overlooking our main dining room. The ambiance is perfect for ladies night out or a casual work event.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 16</li><li>views of open kitchen</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(163,34,'Patio','patio','Situated right on Pennsylvania Ave, just 3.5 blocks from the White House, our spacious patio offers great dining options as well as a hip reception space. Large umbrellas with misters to keep you cool in the summer and heaters for chilly fall nights help guests feel welcome any time of year!','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 75</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 150</li><li>tv</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(164,32,'Wine Cellar','wine-cellar','perfect room for hosting a casual event or formal business meeting, room has stunning views of our exceptional wine selections','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 30</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 50</li><li>flat screen tv  </li><li>vga hook up</li><li>internet access</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(165,32,'News Stand','news-stand','Room is great for smaller groups, able to sit at one table, perfect spot for watching a sporting event or hosting a presentation for a smaller group.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 11</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 12</li><li>flat screen tv  </li><li>vga hook up</li><li>internet access</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(166,33,'Private Wine Room','private-wine-room','Perfect location of intimate occasion, an event to celebration or a corporate function. With two of it\'s four walls incased with hundereds of bottles of wines to select from, this room speaks sophistication.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 30</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 50</li><li>60 inch LCD TVAV capabili</li><li>ties</li><li>Completely Private</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(167,33,'Lower Deck Patio','lower-deck-patio','Great outdoors atmosphere with the just the right mix of hi energy and hospitality.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 65</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 100</li><li>TV&rsquo;s</li><li>custom misting system</li><li>Fire Pit with Heaters</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(168,33,'Summit Bar, Patio and Lounge','patio','The Summit offers Bar, seating and lounge areas. Whether enjoying appetizers and drinks with friends or al fresco dining, with the breathtaking view of the valley and Arizon sunsets this is sure to be your new local hang out.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 100</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 150</li><li>TV&rsquo;s </li><li>custom misting system</li><li>Heaters</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(169,36,'Private Wine Room','private-wine-room','An intimate space perfect for a fully private business meeting to a fun bachelorette party. The warm red and brown tones with windows viewing out to the private patio space will make everyone feel right at home.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 25</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 30</li><li>Flat-screen TV</li><li>Built in Audio Capacities</li><li>Private conneting patio</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(170,37,'PDR','pdr',NULL,'<ul><li>Number of Seats: 20</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 20</li><li>Flat Screen Drop down</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(171,37,'Lounge','lounge',NULL,'</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 30</li><li>FLAT SCREEN COUCHS</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(172,37,'PDR AND LOUNGE','pdr-lounge',NULL,'<ul><li>Number of Seats: 20</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 50</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(173,38,'Wine Room','wine-room','This room Feature a display glass wine cellar','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 16</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 15</li><li>Flat Screen with HD Cable TV</li><li>Built in Audio Visual Capability</li><li>Wired and WiFi Internet</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(174,38,'Poinciana Room','poinciana-room','These 2 room are divided by an Retractable door. Which can enable us to seat 32 guests with Round Tables of 6.','<ul><li>Number of Seats: 16</li><li>Reception Occupancy: 15</li><li>Flat Screen with HD Cable TV</li><li>Built in Audio Visual Capability</li><li>Wired and WiFi Internet</li></ul>',NULL,0,'published'),
	(175,1,'Whole Doulos Room','doulos-whole','<p>Our Doulos Rooms can be sat separately for smaller events of 15-50 or combined for larger scale events of up to 100 guests. Set off from the main dining room helps to ensure a quiet setting for speakers and built in audio visual makes presentations a breeze. Floor-to-ceiling windows allow for natural light and features the hustle and bustle of the Seaport District.</p>','<ul>\n<li>Number of Seats: 90</li>\n<li>Reception Occupancy: 100</li>\n<li>120&rdquo; Screen &amp; Projector</li>\n<li>Built in Audio Capabilities</li>\n</ul>',NULL,0,'published');
