	(8,2,15,0,'the-sure-thing-menu','The Sure Thing - $39 Prix Fixe Menu','','<p><span>Three-courses of both seasonal picks and Sullivan\'s favorites.<br /><br /> Mix &amp; match our starters, soups &amp; salads, and entrees for an incredible meal any day of the week.<br /><br /><br /><a href=\"http://media.dfrg.com/SLV-Insert-May14_T3-T4.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">View Pre-Fixe Menu</a><br /><br /><a href=\"#reservation\" target=\"_blank\">Make a Reservation</a></span></p>','http://media.dfrg.com/SUL-10003_Sure_Thing_Happening_Graphic_600x800.jpg','http://media.dfrg.com/_sullivanssteakhouse/promos/small.jpg','http://media.dfrg.com/_sullivanssteakhouse/promos/sure-thing/medium.jpg',NULL,'http://media.dfrg.com/SUL-Sure Thing Menu_Main.pdf','0000-00-00','2014-09-02','default','published','2013-05-13 11:51:01'),
	(10,1,56,0,NULL,'Power Couple Sundays','$99 Three-Course Dinner for Two','<p>Continued by popular demand, two of our most delicious dishes are getting together for a specially-priced menu for two. Enjoy both our world-famous crab cake and an 8oz filet mignon paired with a crisp salad, signature side dish and house-made dessert for only $99. Enjoy this marriage of great taste. Available Sundays only.</p>','http://media.dfrg.com/DF_Summer_Promo_Poster_General_boston.jpeg',NULL,'http://media.dfrg.com/DF_Summer_Promo_Poster_General_boston.jpeg',NULL,'http://delfriscos.com/media/promos/DF Summer Promo Menus_090611_Web_Boston.pdf','0000-00-00','0000-00-00','default','unpublished','2013-05-13 11:51:01'),
