	(105,3,17,1,'movember','Movember at the Grille','','<img src=\"http://media.dfrg.com/_delfriscosgrille/promos/movember-logo.png\" />\n<p>#manupstacheup</p>\n<p>WHAT IS MOVEMBER? Movember is the month formerly known as November, where men and women across the globe join together to raise awareness and funds for men&rsquo;s health. Men grow and women support a Mo (moustache) for 30 days becoming walking, talking billboards. Movember supports world-class men&rsquo;s health programs that combat prostate and testicular cancer. Go to <a href=\"http://us.movember.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://us.movember.com/</a> for more details.</p>\n<p>HOW IS DEL FRISCO&rsquo;S GRILLE PARTICIPATING IN MOVEMBER? KEEP READING FOR MO DETAILS</p>\n<p>JOIN A DEL FRISCO&rsquo;S GRILLE MOVEMBER TEAM: We have a whole network of teams trying to change the face of men&rsquo;s health. To participate as a Mo Bro (grow a stache!) or Mo Sista,  just join the team of your nearest Del Frisco&rsquo;s Grille location.</p>\n<p>\n<a href=\"http://monetwork.co/DelFriscos\" target=\"_blank\">DEL FRISCO&rsquo;S GRILLE NETWORK</a>\n<ul>\n	<li><a href=\"http://us.movember.com/team/1089233\" target=\"_blank\">Del Frisco&rsquo;s Grille Atlanta</a></li>\n	<li><a href=\"http://us.movember.com/team/1089445\" target=\"_blank\">Del Frisco&rsquo;s Grille Washington, D.C.</a></li>\n	<li><a href=\"http://us.movember.com/team/1089277\" target=\"_blank\">Del Frisco&rsquo;s Grille Dallas</a></li>\n	<li><a href=\"http://us.movember.com/team/1089309\" target=\"_blank\">Del Frisco&rsquo;s Grille Fort Worth</a></li>\n	<li><a href=\"http://us.movember.com/team/1089349\" target=\"_blank\">Del Frisco&rsquo;s Grille Houston</a></li>\n	<li><a href=\"http://us.movember.com/team/1089365\" target=\"_blank\">Del Frisco&rsquo;s Grille New York</a></li>\n	<li><a href=\"http://us.movember.com/team/1089405\" target=\"_blank\">Del Frisco&rsquo;s Grille Phoenix</a></li>\n	<li><a href=\"http://us.movember.com/team/1089417\" target=\"_blank\">Del Frisco&rsquo;s Grille Santa Monica</a></li>\n</ul>\n</p>\n<p>OUR MO MENU: It&rsquo;s Movember at the Grille. We&rsquo;re raising Mo money for men&rsquo;s health, one moustache at a time. For each item ordered from our special Movember menu, we&rsquo;ll donate a percentage of sales to the Movember Foundation.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://media.dfrg.com/_delfriscosgrille/promos/Movember-Menu.pdf\">VIEW MOVEMBER MENU</a></p>\n <p>MOUSTACHE MONDAYS: Real or faux, flash that &lsquo;stache on Mondays in Movember to get a free appetizer. One app per group of four.</p>\n<p>BEST IN MO PHOTO CONTEST &dash; ENTER NOW THROUGH 11/22: Calling all Mo Bros and Mo Sistas, we&rsquo;re looking for the Best in Mo! Visit the Facebook page of your local Del Frisco&rsquo;s Grille location, click on the &ldquo;Best in Mo&rdquo; box and upload a picture of yourself sporting your best moustache or &ldquo;faux mo&rdquo; (that means ladies can enter, too.) for a chance to win dinner for four at the Grille, a year-long health club membership and a grooming package valued at up to $500. Be sure to include a fun title for your photo! Artificial moustaches are allowed for women. Entries will be collected for each Del Frisco&rsquo;s Grille location on the local Del Frisco&rsquo;s Grille Facebook pages and there will be a winner for every location! Your Facebook friends will vote to select each Best in Mo. <a href=\"http://delfriscosgrille.com/BestinMoRules\" target=\"_blank\">Rules and Regulations</a> <br />Click your Grille location to enter:<br />\n<ul>\n	<li><a href=\"http://a.pgtb.me/2XT4SL\" target=\"_blank\">Dallas</a></li>\n	<li><a href=\"http://a.pgtb.me/q6zVjv\" target=\"_blank\">Atlanta</a></li>\n	<li><a href=\"http://a.pgtb.me/0hGj6m\" target=\"_blank\">Fort Worth</a></li>\n	<li><a href=\"http://a.pgtb.me/G6VRWz\" target=\"_blank\">Washington, D.</a></li>\n	<li><a href=\"http://a.pgtb.me/VGcPs2\" target=\"_blank\">Phoenix</a></li>\n	<li><a href=\"http://a.pgtb.me/Pt4jpx\" target=\"_blank\">Santa Monica</a></li>\n	<li><a href=\"http://a.pgtb.me/lrQBnG\" target=\"_blank\">New York</a></li>\n	<li><a href=\"http://a.pgtb.me/5TXLq2\" target=\"_blank\">Houston</a></li>\n</ul></p>','http://media.dfrg.com/_delfriscosgrille/promos/movember-small.png','http://media.dfrg.com/_delfriscosgrille/promos/movember-small.png','http://media.dfrg.com/_delfriscosgrille/promos/movember-promo.png',NULL,'','2013-10-23','2013-11-30','default','unpublished','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
