VALUES
	(1,1,'about','About Del Frisco\'s','<p>Del Frisco&rsquo;s Double Eagle Steak House was born more than 20 years ago. Since then, our vision has remained the same: to embody the rich tradition of the classic American steakhouse, with our impeccable chef-driven cuisine, extensive award-winning wine list and unparalleled hospitality.</p>\n<p>The cornerstone of the Del Frisco&rsquo;s Double Eagle Steak House menu is aged USDA Prime Beef. We serve only the best hand-cut steaks, chops and freshest seafood, including Australian coldwater lobster tails. We use the freshest ingredients to create mouthwatering appetizers, flavorful side dishes and irresistible desserts. Our sommeliers are on hand to guide you through our extensive wine list, and our bartenders will lift your spirits with hand-shaken martinis and handcrafted cocktails. We offer our guests an unforgettable experience in a stunning, energetic atmosphere perfect for special occasions, business affairs or a grand night on the town.</p>'),
	(2,1,'eclub','Join Our E-Club','<p class=\"lead\">Would you like us to keep you informed of the special events and promotions at your favorite Del Frisco\'s? We regularly feature special menus, wine dinners and other special events for our guests. Please complete the form below to receive email updates on events and special offers.</p>'),
	(3,1,'sales','Contact Sales &amp; Event Planner','<p>If you have a special occasion, business meeting or a private party, Del Frisco\'s offers a variety of private and semiprivate dining and reception spaces perfectly suited for any occasion. Del Frisco\'s provides our private diners with warm hospitality and custom menus featuring our finest steak and seafood, as well as personalized beverage service.</p>\n<p>Our dedicated Sales and Event Planners will help you plan and personalize your event so you and your guests can have an unforgettable experience. Please feel free to share details of your upcoming event through the form linked below or call us to make a reservation today.</p>'),
	(4,1,'national','National Private Dining Program','<p>Our National Private Dining Program offers many benefits for companies looking to book multiple events in any of our Sullivan\'s Steakhouse, Del Frisco\'s Double Eagle Steak House and Del Frisco\'s Grille locations. Benefits include a dedicated national point person, inclusive menu packages, rewards and incentive programs, and prearranged A/V.</p>\n<div class=\"text-center\">\r<a href=\"http://media.dfrg.com/_delfriscos/DF_PDmenu/Del Frisco Natl Acct Menus.pdf\">View a PDF of our National Menu</a>\n</div>\r'),
	(5,1,'rewards','Rare Rewards','<p>Everyone likes to get something back. As a Rare Rewards member, you get to do just that. Simply present your card each time you dine with us and earn rewards points. For every dollar spent, you will receive a rewards point. Once accumulated, points can be redeemed for Rewards Dollars, which can be spent in any Sullivan\'s, Del Frisco\'s or Del Frisco\'s Grille across the country.</p>\n<p>The Del Frisco\'s Restaurant Group rewards program is just another way we take care of our loyal guests. Sign up today for a one-time fee of $25 and we will load your Rewards Card with $25 in Rewards Dollars upon registration.</p>\n<p>Reward points may only be redeemed for food and beverage. Redemptions are not valid for tax, gratuity or gift card purchases.</p>\n<div id=\"rewards\" class=\"rewards\">\n<a class=\"reward-link\" href=\"#rewards-01\"><h2 class=\"title\">Reward Levels</h2><i class=\"reward-arrow\"></i></a>\n<div id=\"rewards-01\" class=\"reward-content\">\n<div class=\"description\">\n<h3>Silver Card Level <small>- 10,000 Points</small></h3>\n<p>Once a valued guests reaches this level, they become Silver members. Silver members receive 1.1 points for every dollar spent.</p>\n<h3>Gold Card Level <small>- 25,000 points</small></h3>\n<p>Once a valued guests reach this level, they become Gold members. Gold members receive 1.2 points for every dollar spent.</p>\n<h3>Platinum Card Level <small>- 50,000 points</small></h3>\n<p>Once a valued guest reach this level, they become Platinum members. Platinum members receive 1.3 points for every dollar spent.</p>\n<p>Reward levels are calculated on points earned over the last 12 months and accounts are adjusted monthly. Points can be accumulated at every Sullivan\'s Steakhouse, Del Frisco\'s Double Eagle Steak House and Del Frisco\'s Grille restaurant location.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<a class=\"reward-link\" href=\"#rewards-02\"><h2 class=\"title\">Reward Points</h2><i class=\"reward-arrow\"></i></a>\n<div id=\"rewards-02\" class=\"reward-content\">\n<div class=\"description\">\n<h3>Exceptional Rewards</h3>\n<p>Accumulate 1 point for every dollar spent.</p>\n<ul>\n		<li>350 Points - $25 Reward</li>\n		<li>700 Points - $50 Reward</li>\n		<li>700 Points - Del Frisco&rsquo;s or Sullivan\'s Steak Knives (set of 4 with box)</li>\n		<li>1,400 Points - $100 Reward</li>\n		<li>3,500 Points - $250 Reward</li>\n		<li>7,000 Points - $500 Reward</li>\n		<li>10,000 Points - $700 Reward</li>\n		<li>14,000 Points - $1,000 Reward</li>\n	</ul>\n\n	<p class=\"small\"><em>Please note that the purchase of a Gift Card cannot be applied towards Rewards Points, nor can points be awarded for gratuity.</em></p>\n\n	<p> Rare Rewards dollars can be used for exciting dining experiences at all Del Frisco&rsquo;s Double Eagle Steak House, Sullivan&rsquo;s Steakhouse and Del Frisco&rsquo;s Grille locations. View these dining price range examples to help you plan your next dinner with us, earn rewards points and redeem the rewards dollars that suit your preferences.</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Dinner for two at Del Frisco&rsquo;s Double Eagle Steak House - $225 - $300</li>\n	<li>Dinner for two at Sullivan&rsquo;s Steakhouse - $130 - $175</li>\n	<li>Dinner for two at Del Frisco&rsquo;s Grille - $100 - $150</li>\n	<li>Wine dinner for 10 at Del Frisco&rsquo;s Double Eagle Steak House - $2,800 (approx. starting price)</li>\n	<li>Wine dinner for 10 at Sullivan&rsquo;s Steakhouse - $1,400 (approx. starting price)</li>\n	<li>Wine dinner for 10 at Del Frisco&rsquo;s Grille - $1,200 (approx. starting price)</li>\n</ul>\n\n	</div>\n</div>\n</div>'),
	(6,2,'about','About Sullivan\'s Steakhouse','<p>Sullivan\'s Steakhouse offers an experience unlike any other American steakhouse. From the moment you walk through the door, you will get a feeling that this will be an evening to forget your cares and rekindle romance. Slip into an intimate booth and treat yourself to hand-cut steaks, fresh seafood, signature cocktails and swinging live music. With 19 lively locations across the United States, we offer an evening you won\'t soon forget. If you are looking to flirt with some new flavors, Sullivan\'s will be your sure thing.</p>\n<p>Sullivan\'s proudly serves a well-rounded selection of wine and spirits. Our extensive wine list is a recipient of Wine Spectator\'s \"Award of Excellence\" and offers an array of selections from around the world for everyone from the novice to the wine connoisseur. </p>\n<p>Whether out for business or a personal night with your loved one, it is always our pleasure to be your favorite local steakhouse.</p>\r'),
	(7,2,'sales','Private Dining','<p>If you are celebrating a special occasion for a large group and are looking for a lively, intimate setting, Sullivan\'s offers a variety of private and semiprivate dining and reception spaces perfectly suited for any occasion. Sullivan\'s provides a romantic atmosphere, custom menus featuring our finest steak and seafood, as well as personalized beverage service.</p>\n<p>Our dedicated Sales and Event Planners will help you plan and personalize your event so that you and your guests can enjoy a truly special evening. Get started planning your upcoming event through the form linked below or call us to make a reservation today.</p>\r'),
	(8,2,'national','National Private Dining','<p>Our National Private Dining Program offers many benefits for companies looking to book multiple events in any of our Sullivan\'s Steakhouse, Del Frisco\'s Double Eagle Steak House or Del Frisco\'s Grille locations. Benefits include a dedicated national point person, inclusive menu packages, rewards and incentive programs, and prearranged A/V.</p>\r'),
