	(11,3,'about','About Del Frisco\'s Grille','<p>Modern, inviting, stylish and fun.</p>\n<p>Del Frisco\'s Grille is a modern and fun destination for dining, drinks, socializing and being seen on the scene. The Grille takes the classic America bar and grill concept to refreshing new heights, drawing inspiration from bold flavors and market-fresh ingredients. Everything about us, from the interior design and seating to our exciting food and handcrafted drinks, is built for creating an incredible experience. So pull up a chair and share with your neighbor. </p>\n<p>Our food is over-the-top delicious and is sure to get your friends talking. We dish up creative twists on American comfort classics and serve them to be shared. Each menu includes regional favorites using locally sourced ingredients and features the finest local flavors.</p>\r'),
	(12,3,'sales','Group Dining','<p>Are you getting friends and family together to celebrate a special occasion or just a big night out? Del Frisco&rsquo;s Grille has several exciting options for your crew to meat up and drink up. Large groups can enjoy your own section of the restaurant where you can be catered to while still being part of the vibrant Del Frisco\'s Grille scene. We offer groups customizable menus and friendly service to create an unforgettable evening. </p>\n<p>Our expert Private Dining Coordinator will help you design the perfect event for you and your friends. We can pick out a space within the restaurant that will accommodate all of your needs and create a menu to satisfy every palate and budget. Whether you are getting together with a small group of friends or organizing a big affair, Del Frisco\'s Grille will ensure that your night will be one worth sharing. </p>\r'),
